      "name": "Literature review of published hemolysis power-law correlations",
      "description": "A systematic survey of published hemolysis power-law models (Giersiepen, Zhang, Heuser-Opitz) was conducted to identify best-fit coefficients for the Lagrangian hemolysis accumulation model. Seventeen peer-reviewed publications were reviewed and correlation coefficients were extracted. The review was used to parameterise the CFD hemolysis sub-model and is presented as validation evidence demonstrating agreement between the model's constitutive assumptions and the broader published literature.",
      "activityType": "literature-review"
    }
  ],
  "hasValidationResult": [
    {
